Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.util

Class ImmutableArray<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.util.ImmutableArray<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the component type of the array
All Implemented Interfaces:
Countable, Serializable, Iterable<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ImmutableSet
public class ImmutableArray<T> extends Object implements Iterable<T>, Serializable, Countable
A wrapper around a Java array that makes it read-only and provides some additional helpful methods.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
